reviews.content: Another hit by FoxfortMobile! Makes Safari (and chrome, edge, etc) stop blinding you in low light and gives you a CC toggle for turning it on and off. Extensive dark mode for web browsers on iOS!
Only working safari tweak till October 2020
Partially working on my iPhone 11 Pro on iOS 14.2 using unc0ver. Works in Safari but doesn't seem to be working in other apps.
WebKit.webcontent eats battery with only this tweak on

Works great !
